### Impact
- Provided the CRO with a flexible, data-driven tool for strategic headcount and revenue planning.
- Enabled rapid scenario testing and sensitivity analysis, improving confidence in budget and hiring decisions.
- The model was adopted as a core asset in quarterly planning cycles and contributed to more accurate forecasting and resource allocation.
